{"headeb146g5d77g49e9g9df3g096425ad1c70": ["You know, I think that technically speaking we just did something impossible.", "ad9af97d-75da-406a-ae13-7071c563f604", ".\\dialogs\\Companions\\Reflection_Dialogs\\CRA_MindFlayerControl_RD_ThrallsControlled_Gale.html", "ec6d7a29-66eb-0ca9-71fe-e450e2490565"], "he31f5643g2c65g4f1ag98b7g92b2c19db4e2": ["A mind flayer's hold over its thralls is all but unbreakable. Yet break it we did.", "ad9af97d-75da-406a-ae13-7071c563f604", ".\\dialogs\\Companions\\Reflection_Dialogs\\CRA_MindFlayerControl_RD_ThrallsControlled_Gale.html", "caf68342-2bdb-23c4-d862-4307c71496f8"], "hd3869714ga8dfg4b61gb18bgacf62629614e": ["It was weak - dying even. Doesn't seem so remarkable to me.", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Companions\\Reflection_Dialogs\\CRA_MindFlayerControl_RD_ThrallsControlled_Gale.html", "7e9f16c8-ff6f-9017-449d-90449b069ad5"], "h2f900f2bg99a4g4358ga653g192949387ef8": ["I assure you it was.", "ad9af97d-75da-406a-ae13-7071c563f604", ".\\dialogs\\Companions\\Reflection_Dialogs\\CRA_MindFlayerControl_RD_ThrallsControlled_Gale.html", "cbf1b95d-9d20-2bfb-1c91-073804784a13"], "h21ec8d7cgd5f4g4562g91e2gcecab50467ff": ["The parasite they infected us with: that's the thing that allowed us to do this. But that's not its true function at all.", "ad9af97d-75da-406a-ae13-7071c563f604", ".\\dialogs\\Companions\\Reflection_Dialogs\\CRA_MindFlayerControl_RD_ThrallsControlled_Gale.html", "54fd66cd-b63e-2cc3-e7f5-574ea834cd72"], "h9786f181g7ed4g4d87ga854g7dbe9b75c3f8": ["I'd point out the abnormality of it all, but then again - nothing normal about today.", "ad9af97d-75da-406a-ae13-7071c563f604", ".\\dialogs\\Companions\\Reflection_Dialogs\\CRA_MindFlayerControl_RD_ThrallsControlled_Gale.html", "9607982a-dd54-8b51-3806-def71efce6e8"], "hcc280c9fgb5bag4ab9gbba0ge71803c31626": ["Let's move on.", "ad9af97d-75da-406a-ae13-7071c563f604", ".\\dialogs\\Companions\\Reflection_Dialogs\\CRA_MindFlayerControl_RD_ThrallsControlled_Gale.